    "description": "This spell destroys all of the species that the group of things within the Circle emit in a single direction. It can — for example — make a magus’s traveling party invisible from the direction of another group they wish to ambush. The base level of this spell includes an adjustment that accounts for the magus’s ability to gently move the direction of effect, so that as the enemy group passes by, they cannot spot the hidden party. Other people, for example the members of the magus’s company, can still see each other, because the species reaching their eyes are unobstructed. The transparency requires a Perception + Finesse roll against an Ease Factor of 9 to be convincing.",
